captions.text: -Yo, yo, yo, what's up, fruit lovers?
It's A to the O back with the down-low.
You guys got a ton of questions
and we've got a ton of answers. So, let's get to it!
can you fly using annoyingness as fuel?"
I guess I've never really tried... until now.
-All right, fruit fanatics, let's get to the questions!
-Anything stupid? I can do EVERYTHING stupid.
-(announcer) "Do you ever wish you were a fish?"
-Call off the search, everybody. I'm right here--
Midget Apple would still be the smallest fruit in the kitchen.
Besides, I'm not the smallest anymore
now that my little brother is here to visit.
-Whoa! It's Little Mini Munchkin Midget Apple!
-(announcer) "Will Knife, Iron Fist, and Copper Lincoln
ever start a metal band together?"
-Now, if there's one question that we get all the time,
it's the next one. I guess everyone wants to know...
-(announcer, echoing) Is Marshmallow a boy or a girl?
-Can you tell us whether Marshmallow's a boy or a girl?
-Now that's what I call a "marsh" pit.

-(announcer) "Why did the turkey cross the road?"
-(announcer) "Have you ever been attacked by Pear?"
-Nope, but Midget Apple got attacked by a pear-bear.
-Let's find out. Hey, hey, Master Chef!
-Oh. Hey, Mr. Chief. Hey, Mr. Chief, hey!
-Oh. Hey, Macaroni Cheese! Hey, Macaroni Cheese!
-That doesn't even sound like my name.
Be quiet before I blast you with my assault rifle.

-ZGW would love to be on the Annoying Orange!

-Hey, that's the maniac that chopped down our tree.
-[laughs] Well, I cannot tell a lie.
That's all the questions we have time for this week,
but be sure to leave us some more in the comment area below.
I promise we'll be back next month with more Ask Orange!
-Hey everyone, thanks for watching my brand-new video.
Make sure you like it and favorite it and then send it to everyone
like your mom and your grandpa and your grandpa's dog
and your goldfish and that squirrel outside
and then send it to yourself! Yay! [Captioned by StreamCaptions.com]
